<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="4Jun1930"><font color="red">4 June 1930</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver from Helen Fleischmann): Thank you for &hellip; the clippings about the McCormack film [<i>Song of my heart</i>] &hellip; Mr Joyce is leaving the clinic tomorrow and coming here to the Hotel. I think he will have to remain in Zurich however another week or ten days. Giorgio and I are going back to Paris tomorrow </div>
